{"tid":1261430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母死黑警","createTime":"2019-06-27T08:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:38:53.000Z","uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4fd318956baf74a3be9e8095857b06e0f2b0df","tid":1261430,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"《背水一戰馬拉松路面目測》<br />\n<br />\n香港人最撚叻係打逆境波，<br />\n由六月九號打到今時今日；<br />\n由無乜人理打到萬眾一心；<br />\n由全無希望打到曙光乍現。<br />\n<br />\n請各位唔好自滿，而家嘅局面唔係不勞而獲，<br />\n喺用無數義士嘅汗水；同烈士嘅血淚換番嚟。<br />\n而我哋一班十九大學生，亦會喺接連幾日繼續為香港人提供最新、最準確狗隻動向，<br />\n令各位同路人能夠安身立命，變中求勝。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&lt;<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral%3E&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=f402cbda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;</a></span><br />\n<br />\n想喺不久將來見證條例真正撒回？<br />\n想所有受誣告嘅義士被撒銷控罪？<br />\n想未來依然能夠光明正大喺條街，<br />\n大聲屌鳩港共正苦老母都無人拉？<br />\n麻煩各位喺呢場抗爭馬拉松繼續跑落去。<br />\n<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n自己香港，自己救。"},{"pid":"903dcedadeeb4f1e6a7cb272d095ba48e3bd45c4","tid":1261430,"uid":166595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"跪求 6月份黑警 整合片  (最好有埋字幕)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1261369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1261369</a>"},{"pid":"19b73b0f4f4b107fd8c64439cf1becc16a8baa59","tid":1261430,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1b7931fc1820bc263b1c3b67ccc715e4a596c7a9","tid":1261430,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"838cdc0f568d4b05b2efa8e1e09d5c0130065f49","tid":1261430,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}